{"tid":812854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"超變態！「五年級妹妹用過尿布」 不少賣家留好評","createTime":"2018-09-10T03:38:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T04:17:24.000Z","uid":72009,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"368753e9adde37081f3f1f372f43905640ebc30d","tid":812854,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T03:38:50.000Z","msg":"網路上竟有人在販售「五年級小女生使用過尿布」！<br />\n兒童權益促進協會理事長王薇君，近來發現，竟然有人在露天拍賣販售「用過的尿布」，直呼詭異，質疑有兒少安全疑慮，呼籲警方介入調查！賣家物品名稱還強調「妹妹用過，已經尿濕了,日本大王尿布 xxxL xl(不是M L XL XXL)」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180910/640_c5ec6b79b4690626077441320c30fb0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180910%2F640_c5ec6b79b4690626077441320c30fb0f.jpg&h=d8c192f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180910/640_5d68357387532979990a99ad1f975831.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180910%2F640_5d68357387532979990a99ad1f975831.jpg&h=96841d74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而在商品說明欄則寫道：「為了補貼妹妹布布的錢，只好把用過的布布再次販，讓有需要的人可以再次利用，也謝謝之前幫助妹妹的各位，妹妹換下來的布布都會冰在冷凍，會盡量保持乾淨~謝謝你們。」<br />\n而離奇的是，評價中也有不少已經購買買家留下好評寫道「謝謝,交易愉快!!希望還有機會跟您買東西...」、「值得推薦的好賣家!!!」、「希望下次還有機會和您交易」。<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180910/640_c5ec6b79b4690626077441320c30fb0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180910%2F640_c5ec6b79b4690626077441320c30fb0f.jpg&h=d8c192f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180910/1427126/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180910%2F1427126%2F&d=0AT3V79WG1rIWdgUzk9SNv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=18e28998\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180910%2F1427126%2F&h=26c38b1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180910/1427126/</a>"},{"pid":"bbe15ff158d846d410e5e4e6221295b13f1b5845","tid":812854,"uid":191926,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T03:39:56.000Z","msg":"其實係3x歲毒撚大叔的尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62544c11977301c92e75358bac5074fbe268049f","tid":812854,"uid":26106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T03:41:25.000Z","msg":"淘寶之前屎都有得賣啦"},{"pid":"97c01767175a66e5b6267e5d6f7da7dd160baaed","tid":812854,"uid":36296,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T03:41:38.000Z","msg":"根本就係賣家自己痾尿落去扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dbd370a7b3bb05c2f5092161b85ab63a2f29de0","tid":812854,"uid":31254,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T03:41:42.000Z","msg":"五年級太老，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93bb571c42749cdc032a60014b5a76d2f73ba4d","tid":812854,"uid":79077,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T03:43:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"08a2083132ca3125f5fa270d25b6a75c25fd7d3e","tid":812854,"uid":151717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbe15ff158d846d410e5e4e6221295b13f1b5845","tid":812854,"uid":191926,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T03:39:56.000Z","msg":"其實係3x歲毒撚大叔的尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T03:45:59.000Z","msg":"識法何必破法呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c54d4993412db500891fd4280b5e83ce1121fb13","tid":812854,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62544c11977301c92e75358bac5074fbe268049f","tid":812854,"uid":26106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc